431â†’// ExtractAllModifiedFiles extracts files modified by both the main agent and
432â†’// any subagents spawned via the Task tool. It parses the main transcript from
433â†’// startLine, collects modified files from the main agent, then reads each
434â†’// subagent's transcript from subagentsDir to collect their modified files too.
435â†’// The result is a deduplicated list of all modified file paths.
436â†’func ExtractAllModifiedFiles(transcriptPath string, startLine int, subagentsDir string) ([]string, error) {
437â†’	if transcriptPath == "" {
